; Mathomatic configuration file for Microsoft Windows,
; other systems use the file name "~/.mathomaticrc".

; This file ("mathomatic.rc") belongs in the same directory as "mathomatic.exe".

; You can use this file to permanently configure "set" variables.

; Enable bold color mode every time Mathomatic is run:
bold color

; To see the current configuration when using Mathomatic type
